		{"id":"3703a4e9d0edf2b1","type":"text","text":"карты персонажа\n\nid\npersonId\ncardId:\nулучшения карты: {\n\n}\n\n","x":-620,"y":-120,"width":250,"height":440},
		{"id":"e625921bdc1989ac","type":"text","text":"Наложенные заклинания на персонажа\n\nid\ncardId:\npesonId\nистощения процен\nвремя начала действия\nвремя окончания действия\n\n","x":-290,"y":-120,"width":250,"height":440},
		{"id":"cf9464f3213198a3","type":"text","text":"Сначалал все принимает щит\nпотом доспех\n","x":460,"y":30,"width":250,"height":140},
		{"id":"af3682b96e4ce153","type":"text","text":"Атакующие заклинания\n\n```\nid\ncardId\ndamage: единоразово 20%\ndurationDamage: 20% (за раунд раунд 3с поумолчанию)\ndamageAreа: radius 5 steps\ngradient : 10% это ослабление на каждые 10% от центра\ndamageType: {\n\t  phisical: 10%\n\t  flame: 10%\n\t  water: 10%\n\t  air: 10%\n\t  earth: 10%\n\t  dark: 10%\n\t  light: 10%\n}\nduration: 5\n```","x":330,"y":440,"width":520,"height":500},
		{"id":"a02c1abc7525dec4","type":"text","text":"**Карты**\n\nid (Автоинкремент, первичный ключ)\nname ()\ntype ()\nperiod: 30 days\nrang: GOLD\nrarety: редкая\n\n\n\n","x":-640,"y":440,"width":400,"height":320},
		{"id":"0b9dfa0383993851","type":"text","text":"Щиты\n\nid\ncardId\nresitences:{\n  phisical: middle\n  flame: low\n  water: middle\n  air: high\n  earth: high\n  dark: high\n  light: high\n}\nduration: 8 h","x":-160,"y":440,"width":400,"height":380},
		{"id":"08d3c07fa0a284f8","type":"text","text":"Доспехи\n\nid\ncardId\nresitences:{\n  phisical: minimal, low, middle, good, excelent ( 1-5)\n  flame: \n  water: \n  air: \n  earth: \n  dark: \n  light: \n}\nduration: 8 h","x":-160,"y":860,"width":400,"height":420},
		{"id":"d1fd5bda6801ae33","type":"text","text":"Усилители защиты\n\nid\ncardId\nщит: 20 %\nдоспех 20%\nduration: 8 h","x":-160,"y":1320,"width":400,"height":280},
